></div></div></div><div style=\"border-left:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);padding:14px\"><div style=\"font-size:8px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-bottom:10px;letter-spacing:0.1em\">9-FACTOR CONFLUENCE</div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px\"><div style=\"width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:#00ff88;flex-shrink:0\"></div><span style=\"flex:1;font-size:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">RSI-14</span><span style=\"font-size:8px;font-weight:700;color:#00ff88\">BULL</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px\"><div style=\"width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:#00ff88;flex-shrink:0\"></div><span style=\"flex:1;font-size:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">MACD</span><span style=\"font-size:8px;font-weight:700;color:#00ff88\">BULL</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px\"><div style=\"width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:#ff4466;flex-shrink:0\"></div><span style=\"flex:1;font-size:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">Bollinger</span><span style=\"font-size:8px;font-weight:700;color:#ff4466\">BEAR</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px\"><div style=\"width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:#ff4466;flex-shrink:0\"></div><span style=\"flex:1;font-size:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">Stochastic %K</span><span style=\"font-size:8px;font-weight:700;color:#ff4466\">BEAR</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px\"><div style=\"width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:#ff4466;flex-shrink:0\"></div><span style=\"flex:1;font-size:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">Volume</span><span style=\"font-size:8px;font-weight:700;color:#ff4466\">BEAR</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px\"><div style=\"width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:#ff4466;flex-shrink:0\"></div><span style=\"flex:1;font-size:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">SMA Cross</span><span style=\"font-size:8px;font-weight:700;color:#ff4466\">BEAR</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px\"><div style=\"width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:#00ff88;flex-shrink:0\"></div><span style=\"flex:1;font-size:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">vs SMA20</span><span style=\"font-size:8px;font-weight:700;color:#00ff88\">BULL</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px\"><div style=\"width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:#ff4466;flex-shrink:0\"></div><span style=\"flex:1;font-size:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">52W Position</span><span style=\"font-size:8px;font-weight:700;color:#ff4466\">BEAR</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px\"><div style=\"width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:#00ff88;flex-shrink:0\"></div><span style=\"flex:1;font-size:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">5D Momentum</span><span style=\"font-size:8px;font-weight:700;color:#00ff88\">BULL</span></div><div style=\"margin-top:14px;background:rgba(0,170,255,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(0,170,255,0.15);border-radius:6px;padding:10px\"><div style=\"font-size:7px;color:#00aaff;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;letter-spacing:0.1em\">QUANT RAG REASONING</div><div style=\"font-size:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);line-height:1.6;font-style:italic\">&quot;Signal aligns with time series momentum theory — mean reversion indicators suggest...&quot;</div></div></div></div></div></section><section style=\"padding:40px 24px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.01)\"><div style=\"max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4, 1fr);gap:24px;text-align:center\"><div><div style=\"font-size:clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px);font-weight:800;color:#00ff88\">86</div><div style=\"font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin-top:4px;letter-spacing:0.08em\">Assets Covered</div></div><div><div style=\"font-size:clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px);font-weight:800;color:#00ff88\">67.8%</div><div style=\"font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin-top:4px;letter-spacing:0.08em\">Backtest Win Rate</div></div><div><div style=\"font-size:clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px);font-weight:800;color:#00ff88\">2.87</div><div style=\"font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin-top:4px;letter-spacing:0.08em\">Sharpe Ratio</div></div><div><div style=\"font-size:clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px);font-weight:800;color:#00ff88\">21</div><div style=\"font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin-top:4px;letter-spacing:0.08em\">ML Features</div></div></div></section><section id=\"proof\" style=\"padding:80px 24px\"><div style=\"max-width:900px;margin:0 auto\"><div style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:56px\"><h2 style=\"font-size:clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);font-weight:800;margin-bottom:12px;color:#fff\">We don&#x27;t ask you to trust us</h2><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.05em\">WE SHOW YOU THE BACKTEST. YOU DECIDE.</p></div><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));gap:16px\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;padding:24px\"><div style=\"color:#00ff88;margin-bottom:16px\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-no-axes-column\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 21v-6\"></path><path d=\"M12 21V3\"></path><path d=\"M19 21V9\"></path></svg></div><h3 style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;color:#fff\">Walk-Forward Validated</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);font-size:12px;line-height:1.8\">6-month walk-forward validation with no lookahead bias. Every signal is tested against data the model never saw during training.</p></div><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;padding:24px\"><div style=\"color:#00ff88;margin-bottom:16px\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-brain\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 18V5\"></path><path d=\"M15 13a4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3-4 4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3 4\"></path><path d=\"M17.598 6.5A3 3 0 1 0 12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.598 1.5\"></path><path d=\"M17.997 5.125a4 4 0 0 1 2.526 5.77\"></path><path d=\"M18 18a4 4 0 0 0 2-7.464\"></path><path d=\"M19.967 17.483A4 4 0 1 1 12 18a4 4 0 1 1-7.967-.517\"></path><path d=\"M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-2-7.464\"></path><path d=\"M6.003 5.125a4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77\"></path></svg></div><h3 style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;color:#fff\">XGBoost + LightGBM</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);font-size:12px;line-height:1.8\">Two-model ensemble trained on 2 years of OHLCV data per asset. Probability calibrated with isotonic regression.</p></div><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;padding:24px\"><div style=\"color:#00ff88;margin-bottom:16px\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><h3 style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;color:#fff\">ATR-Based Risk Levels</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);font-size:12px;line-height:1.8\">Take Profit and Stop Loss set by Average True Range — volatility-adjusted for each asset, not arbitrary percentages.</p></div></div></div></section><section style=\"padding:80px 24px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.01);border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05)\"><div style=\"max-width:900px;margin:0 auto\"><div style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:56px\"><h2 style=\"font-size:clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);font-weight:800;margin-bottom:12px;color:#fff\">Everything in one place</h2><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.05em\">NO OTHER RETAIL TOOL COMBINES ALL FIVE OF THESE.</p></div><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));gap:12px\"><div style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:10px;padding:18px\"><div style=\"width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(0,255,136,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(0,255,136,0.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#00ff88\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:6px;color:#fff;letter-spacing:0.03em\">ML Signal + Probability</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);line-height:1.7\">BUY/SELL/HOLD with an actual probability score, not just a direction.</div></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:10px;padding:18px\"><div style=\"width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(0,255,136,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(0,255,136,0.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#00ff88\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:6px;color:#fff;letter-spacing:0.03em\">9-Factor Confluence</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);line-height:1.7\">RSI, MACD, Bollinger, Stochastic, Volume, SMA Cross, 52W Position, Momentum — all in one scorecard.</div></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:10px;padding:18px\"><div style=\"width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(0,255,136,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(0,255,136,0.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#00ff88\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:6px;color:#fff;letter-spacing:0.03em\">Kelly Criterion Sizing</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);line-height:1.7\">Exact position size based on your edge and risk/reward ratio. Not a fixed 1% or 2%.</div></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:10px;padding:18px\"><div style=\"width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(0,255,136,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(0,255,136,0.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#00ff88\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:6px;color:#fff;letter-spacing:0.03em\">LLM Reasoning</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);line-height:1.7\">Groq-powered plain-English explanation of every signal. Know why, not just what.</div></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:10px;padding:18px\"><div style=\"width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(0,255,136,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(0,255,136,0.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#00ff88\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:6px;color:#fff;letter-spacing:0.03em\">Live News Sentiment</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);line-height:1.7\">7 RSS feeds scored and blended into the ML signal in real time.</div></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:10px;padding:18px\"><div style=\"width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(0,255,136,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(0,255,136,0.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#00ff88\" stroke-width=